Micrometer library

https://docs.spring.io/spring-metrics/docs/current/public/prometheus
https://docs.spring.io/spring-boot/docs/current/reference/html/actuator.html#actuator.metrics
---------------------------------------------------
How to access metrics from UI:
http://127.0.0.1:8080/actuator/
http://127.0.0.1:8080/actuator/metrics
http://127.0.0.1:8080/actuator/metrics/hello

to increase metric - simply visite utl:
http://127.0.0.1:8080/hello
---------------------------------------------------
Counter - simle increment that can be reset to 0
Gauge - could be decremented and incremented (almost same to gauge)


